content: Like Crooked Joe Biden, who has WEAPONIZED GOVERNMENT AGAINST HIS POLITICAL OPPONENT, Crazy Kamala Harris is a LOW I.Q. INDIVIDUAL who cannot compete with the leaders of other countries. Like Sleepy Joe before her, she can’t put two sentences together!!!
